Superman Family Adventures (001 - 012) (2012 - 2013) (Digital) (Empire)


Superman Family Adventures, a new ongoing all ages series by Eisner Award-winning Tiny Titans creative team, Art Baltazar and Franco. The series will be starring the whole Superman gang; Superman, Supergirl, Superboy, Lois Lane, Jimmy Olsen, Lex Luthor, Bizarro, General Zod and Fuzzy the Krypto Mouse!
